PC Timer is a free desktop application that helps you automatically shutdown, restart, or log off your computer after a set time.

You just enter the number of hours and minutes, and the software will:

-Calculate the exact time the action will happen
-View the exact execution time
-Automatically perform the selected action when time is up

It is designed to be simple, fast, and easy to use, with no complicated settings.

PC Timer works on Windows 8, 10, and 11, and does not require an internet connection.

🎉 Completely free for everyone to use
